{Scorpina}

    She slowly turned a shine shifting across the purple optics as she
noticed the hand edging towards a weapon considering her new body she
wondered what armaments it might have but still if the maximal/predicon
skirmishes were still going on it would be best not to make enemies yet...

    Shrugging she smiled, "No faction as of yet, I'm a mercenary by
profession...and which are you Maximal or Predicon?"
